##Seed_(co-)orthologs: ## type: type of orthology(one2one, one2many, many2one, many2many)
## treefile: name of the tree file
## source: Pfam for pfamA famlies or MMseqs for mmseqs families (these families were built with mmseq clustering with members that doesnt have any pfam domain)

## FamName: is the name of the family, can be a Domain name if is a PfamA family (e.g. Thioredoxin_14) or a name of a sequence for mmseqs family (e.g. 35128.B8C3S0. mmseqs  picks one random sequence name for naming the family)
## PfrenName: is the name that eggnog-mapper gives to the seed sequence
## GeneName_seed: gene name of seed sequence  from uniprot/ensembl
## GeneName_target:  gene name of target sequence from uniprot/ensembl
## OG_euk: OG at eukarya level in which seed sequence is present
## target_species: scientific name of the target sequence
